name: asynqmon
description: Real-time monitor and web admin for Asynq distributed task queue
full_description:
Docker image for [Asynqmon](https://github.com/hibiken/asynqmon)

Asynqmon is a web based tool for monitoring and administrating [Asynq](https://github.com/hibiken/asynq) queues and tasks.

### Usage

```
docker run --rm \
    -p 8080:8080
    hibiken/asynqmon --redis-addr=host.docker.internal:6379
```
